reviewText: The disk worked great no damage happy with this product
I love the manga and I wanted to get into the anime. Well, I did and it's just as good as the manga! =)

Volume 2 introduces more characters to the show.  My sons and I really enjoy this series.  It has likeable charaters, light humor and, since we also watch Naruto, familiar voices.  It is a show for entertainment.
It was awesome and volume 1 came with a poster so it was cool it had Ginta and bowbo on the front and on the back a map of mar
